Package com.opengamma.strata.collect.function

Interface ObjDoublePredicate<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the object parameter
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
    @FunctionalInterface
public interface ObjDoublePredicate<T>
    A predicate of two arguments - one object and one double.

    This takes two arguments and returns a boolean result.

    See Also:
    BiPredicate
